Get VI:Qualified Name Method

Short Name: Get VI.Qualified Name

Requires: Base Development System

Class: Application Methods

To Use: Create a method.

Returns the qualified name of the referenced VI without loading the VI.

Parameters

Data typeNameRequiredDescription
VI PathYesPath to the VI whose help information you want to get.
VI Qualified NameYesQualified name of the VI.

Remarks

The following table lists the characteristics of this method.

Data typeNo return value

Remote access allowedYes
